INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("3648", "4", "2016-03-21 15:47:17", "2016-03-21 15:47:17", "[vc_row type=\"full_width_background\" bg_position=\"left top\" bg_repeat=\"no-repeat\" text_color=\"custom\" text_align=\"center\" scene_position=\"center\" layer_one_image=\"2518\" top_padding=\"0\" bottom_padding=\"0\" layer_four_image=\"2655\" id=\"home\" bg_color=\"#ffffff\" custom_text_color=\"#ababab\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\" animation=\"none\" column_padding=\"no-extra-padding\" column_padding_position=\"all\" background_color=\"#ffffff\" background_color_opacity=\"1\" font_color=\"#ababab\" centered_text=\"true\"][nectar_slider location=\"Home\" full_width=\"true\" fullscreen=\"true\" arrow_navigation=\"true\" desktop_swipe=\"true\" loop=\"true\" slider_transition=\"fade\" parallax=\"true\" slider_button_styling=\"btn_with_count\" overall_style=\"classic\" button_sizing=\"large\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][heading]\r\n<h1></h1>\r\n<h1>Marketing &amp; Advertising Agency in Detroit, MI</h1>\r\n[/heading][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row type=\"full_width_background\" bg_position=\"left top\" bg_repeat=\"no-repeat\" text_color=\"dark\" text_align=\"center\" parallax_bg=\"true\" scene_position=\"center\" vertically_center_columns=\"true\" top_padding=\"8%\" bottom_padding=\"4%\" bg_color=\"#ffffff\" id=\"Strategy\" exclude_row_header_color_inherit=\"true\" class=\"Strategy\"][vc_column width=\"1/4\" animation=\"none\" column_padding=\"no-extra-padding\" background_color_opacity=\"1\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/1\" enable_animation=\"true\" animation=\"grow-in\" delay=\"0\" column_padding=\"no-extra-padding\" centered_text=\"true\"][vc_column_text][icon size=\"large\" image=\"icon-tablet\" color=\"Extra-Color-1\"][/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_column_text]\r\n<h4>Launch</h4>\r\nYour product is awesome, but you have no idea to take it to market. We\'ll help you discover and build your marketing plan and funnel so you can start generating real business.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\" animation=\"none\" column_padding=\"no-extra-padding\" background_color_opacity=\"1\" delay=\"200\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/1\" enable_animation=\"true\" animation=\"grow-in\" delay=\"200\" column_padding=\"no-extra-padding\" centered_text=\"true\"][vc_column_text][icon color=\"Extra-Color-1\" size=\"large\" image=\"steadysets-icon-diamond\" ][/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_column_text]\r\n<h4>Acquisition</h4>\r\nDiscovering the right advertising channels and campaigns can be time consuming. We have deep experience and will help you launch and optimize to make sure you\'re never wasting time and money.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\" animation=\"none\" column_padding=\"no-extra-padding\" background_color_opacity=\"1\" delay=\"400\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/1\" enable_animation=\"true\" animation=\"grow-in\" delay=\"400\" column_padding=\"no-extra-padding\" centered_text=\"true\"][vc_column_text][icon size=\"large\" image=\"linecon-icon-display\" color=\"Extra-Color-1\"][/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_column_text]\r\n<h4>Optimization</h4>\r\nYou need to a/b test, dive deep into your numbers, and set up all of the right marketing tools, but you have no idea where to start. We\'ll help you get set up the right way, the first time.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\" animation=\"none\" column_padding=\"no-extra-padding\" background_color_opacity=\"1\" delay=\"600\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/1\" enable_animation=\"true\" animation=\"grow-in\" delay=\"600\" column_padding=\"no-extra-padding\" centered_text=\"true\"][vc_column_text][icon size=\"large\" image=\"icon-gift\" color=\"Extra-Color-1\"][/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_column_text]\r\n<h4>Analysis</h4>\r\nYour campaigns are live and traffic leads are coming in. It\'s time to find out who those leads are and how you can find more of them. Our data analysts will dive deep into your data to help you scale.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row type=\"full_width_background\" bg_position=\"center bottom\" bg_repeat=\"no-repeat\" text_color=\"dark\" text_align=\"left\" top_padding=\"8%\" bottom_padding=\"100\" bg_color=\"#ffffff\" scene_position=\"center\" exclude_row_header_color_inherit=\"true\" id=\"Services\"][vc_column width=\"1/3\" enable_animation=\"true\" animation=\"fade-in\" delay=\"0\" column_padding=\"no-extra-padding\" background_color_opacity=\"1\"][text-with-icon icon_type=\"font_icon\" icon=\"linecon-icon-lab\" color=\"Extra-Color-3\"]\r\n<h4>SEO</h4>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Technical optimization of our clients’ sites, on-site content creation to develop breadth, depth, and authority, and generation of branded and non-branded off-site content to raise awareness, drive traffic, and boost user engagement, rankings, and ROI.</span></p>\r\n[/text-with-icon][divider line_type=\"No Line\" custom_height=\"20\"][text-with-icon icon_type=\"font_icon\" icon=\"linecon-icon-display\" color=\"Extra-Color-3\"]\r\n<h4>Conversion Optimization</h4>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Figuring out how to drive the right person to your site at the right time is where you likely spend 90% of your brainpower and 99% of your media dollars. We embrace the wholly underused tactic that is endless optimization of sites and landing pages to improve conversions.</span></p>\r\n[/text-with-icon][text-with-icon icon_type=\"font_icon\" icon=\"linecon-icon-pen\" color=\"Extra-Color-3\"]\r\n<h4>Content Marketing</h4>\r\nContent marketing is not a product unto itself. Instead, it lies at the heart of every piece of marketing material and in every touch point of the customer journey. From infographics to ego bait and scholarship campaigns, every angle is explored for our clients to achieve an authoritative and appealing voice in the competitive online space.[/text-with-icon][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\" enable_animation=\"true\" animation=\"fade-in\" delay=\"200\" column_padding=\"no-extra-padding\" background_color_opacity=\"1\"][text-with-icon icon_type=\"font_icon\" icon=\"steadysets-icon-tag\" color=\"Extra-Color-3\"]\r\n<h4>Paid Search</h4>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">An understanding of what makes people click and purchase, an obsession with testing ads and messaging, and embracing the multi-touch, multi-device path to conversion are all required for our clients’ paid search and display campaigns to outperform their peers.</span></p>\r\n[/text-with-icon][divider line_type=\"No Line\" custom_height=\"20\"][text-with-icon icon_type=\"font_icon\" icon=\"linecon-icon-like\" color=\"Extra-Color-3\"]\r\n<h4>Social Advertising</h4>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Your next customer and ultimately unlimited growth potential can be discovered through a social platform. In order to turn feed browsers into customers, you need to reach the right person with the right message at the right time. We makes this happen.</span></p>\r\n[/text-with-icon][text-with-icon icon_type=\"font_icon\" icon=\"steadysets-icon-phone\" color=\"Extra-Color-3\"]\r\n<h4>Mobile Advertising</h4>\r\nWith computing power and user experience quality paving the way, mobile almost overnight became a medium that produces powerful results and measurable ROI. At Marketing Supply Company, we view the mobile opportunity as far more than an afterthought. We recognize these devices that never leave our sides also present a massive opportunity for our clients to grow their sales, leads, and businesses. We take advantage of the unique features of mobile – location, social interaction, and intent – to produce custom initiatives and outsized results.[/text-with-icon][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\" enable_animation=\"true\" animation=\"fade-in\" delay=\"400\" column_padding=\"no-extra-padding\" background_color_opacity=\"1\"][text-with-icon icon_type=\"font_icon\" icon=\"steadysets-icon-graph\" color=\"Extra-Color-3\"]\r\n<h4>Growth Strategy</h4>\r\nTo grow your business successfully, you need a growth strategy that is ahead of the market. Our team will help you figure out what that strategy is, and show you how to take it to market.[/text-with-icon][divider line_type=\"No Line\" custom_height=\"40\"][text-with-icon icon_type=\"font_icon\" icon=\"linecon-icon-user\" color=\"Extra-Color-3\"]\r\n<h4>Marketing Team Training</h4>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Our experts will sit down with your team and train them on how to become a better marketer. From the tools they need to learn to love, to the best tactics for ad purchasing, we can pass this valuable information along so you can scale your business successfully.</span></p>\r\n[/text-with-icon][text-with-icon icon_type=\"font_icon\" icon=\"linecon-icon-bulb\" color=\"Extra-Color-3\"]\r\n<h4>Affiliate Marketing</h4>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">Becoming an industry leader in attribution, affiliate engagement, and new affiliate recruitment, Our approach pairs sophisticated strategy with white-glove service to drive success for you business.</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n.[/text-with-icon][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row type=\"full_width_background\" bg_position=\"left top\" bg_repeat=\"no-repeat\" bg_color=\"#ffffff\" scene_position=\"center\" text_color=\"dark\" text_align=\"left\" top_padding=\"2%\" bottom_padding=\"8%\" id=\"customers\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\" animation=\"none\" column_padding=\"padding-3-percent\" column_padding_position=\"right\" background_color_opacity=\"1\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\" animation=\"none\" column_padding=\"no-extra-padding\" column_padding_position=\"all\"][image_with_animation image_url=\"3388\" animation=\"Flip In\" img_link_target=\"_self\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"3/4\" animation=\"none\" column_padding=\"padding-3-percent\" column_padding_position=\"left\"][vc_column_